INSERT INTO `Background` VALUES ('198','Deneith Mercenary','House Deneith','Eberron','History, Intimidate','Eberron Player\'s Guide','0','\r\n\r\n<!DOCTYPE HTML>\r\n<html>\r\n<head id=\"Head1\"><title>\r\nDeneith Mercenary\r\n</title><meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=EmulateIE7\" /><link href=\"styles/detail.css\" media=\"screen\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" /><link href=\"styles/print.css\" media=\"print\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" /><link href=\"styles/mobile.css\" media=\"handheld\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n    <form name=\"form1\" method=\"post\" action=\"display.php?page=background&amp;id=198\" id=\"form1\">\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n    <div id=\"detail\">\r\n\r\n<h1   class=\"player\">Deneith Mercenary</h1><p class=\"flavortext\"><b>Type: </b>House Deneith<br/><b>Campaign Setting: </b>Eberron<br/></p>You served with House Deneith’s Blademarks Guild during the Last War. What major battles did you take part in, and on which side? Were you ever wounded, and do you still bear the physical or mental scars? Were you ever captured, besieged, or caught behind enemy lines? How would you characterize your relationship with your commanding officer?<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<i>Associated Skills: </i>History, Intimidate<br/><p class=\"publishedIn\">Published in <a href=\"http://anonym.to/?http://www.wizards.com/default.asp?x=products/dndacc/9780786951000\" target=\"_new\">Eberron Player\'s Guide</a>, page(s) 153.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </form>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\n    if (document.all) {\r\n        if (document.documentMode != 9) {\r\n            var ar = document.getElementsByTagName(\'span\');\r\n            for (var i = 0; i < ar.length; i++ ) {\r\n                var c = ar[i].attributes[\'class\'].value;\r\n                if (c == \'milevel\')\r\n                    ar[i].style.top = \"-24px\";\r\n          