INSERT INTO `Background` VALUES ('344','Salvation','Racial','General','Intimidate, Religion','Dragon Magazine 380','0','\r\n\r\n<!DOCTYPE HTML>\r\n<html>\r\n<head id=\"Head1\"><title>\r\nSalvation\r\n</title><meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=EmulateIE7\" /><link href=\"styles/detail.css\" media=\"screen\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" /><link href=\"styles/print.css\" media=\"print\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" /><link href=\"styles/mobile.css\" media=\"handheld\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n    <form name=\"form1\" method=\"post\" action=\"display.php?page=background&amp;id=344\" id=\"form1\">\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n    <div id=\"detail\">\r\n\r\n<h1   class=\"player\">Salvation</h1><p class=\"flavortext\"><b>Type: </b>Racial<br/><b>Campaign Setting: </b>General<br/><b>Prerequisite: </b>Shadar-Kai<br/></p>All shadar-kai face oblivion, because that is the price exacted by the Raven Queen for being spared age and its infirmities. What do you think the Raven Queen will grant you by serving her? Do you want to escape the oblivion altogether or just forestall it? Do you hope to be chosen to serve as her sorrowsworn? Do you resent the deity?<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<i>Associated Skills: </i>Intimidate, Religion<br/><p class=\"publishedIn\">Published in <a href=\"http://anonym.to/?http://www.wizards.com/default.asp?x=dnd/drtoc/380\" target=\"_new\">Dragon Magazine 380</a>, page(s) 58.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </form>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\n    if (document.all) {\r\n        if (document.documentMode != 9) {\r\n            var ar = document.getElementsByTagName(\'span\');\r\n            for (var i = 0; i < ar.length; i++ ) {\r\n                var c = ar[i].attributes[\'class\'].value;\r\n                if (c == \'milevel\')\r\n                    ar[i].style.top = \"-24px\";\r\n                else if (c == \'miright\')