INSERT INTO `Background` VALUES ('517','Heartless Mercenary','Racial','Dark Sun','Acrobatics, Stealth','Dark Sun Campaign Setting','0','\r\n\r\n<!DOCTYPE HTML>\r\n<html>\r\n<head id=\"Head1\"><title>\r\nHeartless Mercenary\r\n</title><meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=EmulateIE7\" /><link href=\"styles/detail.css\" media=\"screen\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" /><link href=\"styles/print.css\" media=\"print\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" /><link href=\"styles/mobile.css\" media=\"handheld\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n    <form name=\"form1\" method=\"post\" action=\"display.php?page=background&amp;id=517\" id=\"form1\">\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n    <div id=\"detail\">\r\n\r\n<h1   class=\"player\">Heartless Mercenary</h1><p class=\"flavortext\"><b>Type: </b>Racial<br/><b>Campaign Setting: </b>Dark Sun<br/><b>Prerequisite: </b>Half-elf<br/></p>Finding no practical line of work in your community, you resorted to less noble means to make ends meet—you became a professional killer. Did you operate in the open, or did you conceal your true work behind a cover profession? Do you still kill for coin? If not, why did you stop? How do you look back on your time as a sellsword?<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<i>Associated Skills: </i>Acrobatics, Stealth<br/><p class=\"publishedIn\">Published in <a href=\"http://anonym.to/?http://www.wizards.com/dnd/Product.php?x=dnd/products/dndacc/253870000\" target=\"_new\">Dark Sun Campaign Setting</a>, page(s) 28.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </form>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\n    if (document.all) {\r\n        if (document.documentMode != 9) {\r\n            var ar = document.getElementsByTagName(\'span\');\r\n            for (var i = 0; i < ar.length; i++ ) {\r\n                var c = ar[i].attributes[\'class\'].value;\r\n                if (c == \'milevel\')\r\n                    ar[i].style.top = \"-24px\";\r\n                else if (c == \'miright\')\r\n                    ar[i].style.top = \"-18px\";\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n</script>\r\n');
INSERT INTO `Background` VALUES ('518','Nature\'s Protector','Racial','Dark Sun','Heal, Nature','Dark Sun Campaign Setting','0','\r\n\r\n<!DOCTYPE HTML>\r\n<html>\r\n<head id=\"Head1\"><title>\r\nNature\'s Protector\r\n</title><meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=EmulateIE7\" /><link href=\"styles/detail.css\" media=\"screen\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" /><link href=\"styles/print.css\" media=\"print\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" /><link href=\"styles/mobile.css\" media=\"handheld\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n    <form name=\"form1\" method=\"post\" action=\"display.php?page=background&amp;id=518\" id=\"form1\">\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n    <div id=\"detail\">\r\n\r\n<h1   class=\"player\">Nature\'s Protector</h1><p class=\"flavortext\"><b>Type: </b>Racial<br/><b>Campaign Setting: </b>Dark Sun<br/><b>Prerequisite: </b>Halfling<br/></p>You commit your life to protecting the few natural resources left in the world. Is this task inherited from a predecessor, or did you assume the burden on your own? How do you protect nature? Do you guard a particular site, or do you watch over all lands through which you travel? In your mind, what is the greatest threat to nature?<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<i>Associated Skills: </i>Heal, Nature<br/><p class=\"publishedIn\">Published in <a href=\"http://anonym.to/?http://www.wizards.com/dnd/Product.php?x=dnd/products/dndacc/253870000\" target=\"_new\">Dark Sun Campaign Setting</a>, page(s) 28.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </form>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\n    if (document.all) {\r\n        if (document.documentMode != 9) {\r\n            var ar = document.getElementsByTagName(\'span\');\r\n            for (var i = 0; i < ar.length; i++ ) {\r\n                var c = ar[i].attributes[\'class\'].value;\r\n                if (c == \'milevel\')\r\n                    ar[i].style.top = \"-24px\";\r\