INSERT INTO `Background` VALUES ('644','Raam - Dedicated Rebel','Geography','Dark Sun','Religion, Streetwise','Dark Sun Campaign Setting','0','\r\n\r\n<!DOCTYPE HTML>\r\n<html>\r\n<head id=\"Head1\"><title>\r\nRaam - Dedicated Rebel\r\n</title><meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=EmulateIE7\" /><link href=\"styles/detail.css\" media=\"screen\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" /><link href=\"styles/print.css\" media=\"print\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" /><link href=\"styles/mobile.css\" media=\"handheld\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n    <form name=\"form1\" method=\"post\" action=\"display.php?page=background&amp;id=644\" id=\"form1\">\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n    <div id=\"detail\">\r\n\r\n<h1   class=\"player\">Raam - Dedicated Rebel</h1><p class=\"flavortext\"><b>Type: </b>Geography<br/><b>Campaign Setting: </b>Dark Sun<br/></p>You fight alongside other disaffected citizens, battling the templars and mansabdars to oust Abalach-Re and right the city’s course. Were you recruited, or do you fight alone? Why did you join the uprising? Can you move freely about Raam, or are you hunted for your part in the rebellion?<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<i>Associated Skills: </i>Religion, Streetwise<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<i>Associated Languages: </i>Elven<br/><p class=\"publishedIn\">Published in <a href=\"http://anonym.to/?http://www.wizards.com/dnd/Product.php?x=dnd/products/dndacc/253870000\" target=\"_new\">Dark Sun Campaign Setting</a>, page(s) 168.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </form>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\n    if (document.all) {\r\n        if (document.documentMode != 9) {\r\n            var ar = document.getElementsByTagName(\'span\');\r\n            for (var i = 0; i < ar.length; i++ ) {\r\n                var c = ar[i].attributes[\'class\'].value;\r\n                if (c == \'milevel\')\r\n                    ar[i].style.top