INSERT INTO `Background` VALUES ('698','Aberrant Slayer','Racial','General','Dungeoneering, Perception','Psionic Power','0','\r\n\r\n<!DOCTYPE HTML>\r\n<html>\r\n<head id=\"Head1\"><title>\r\nAberrant Slayer\r\n</title><meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=EmulateIE7\" /><link href=\"styles/detail.css\" media=\"screen\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" /><link href=\"styles/print.css\" media=\"print\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" /><link href=\"styles/mobile.css\" media=\"handheld\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n    <form name=\"form1\" method=\"post\" action=\"display.php?page=background&amp;id=698\" id=\"form1\">\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n    <div id=\"detail\">\r\n\r\n<h1   class=\"player\">Aberrant Slayer</h1><p class=\"flavortext\"><b>Type: </b>Racial<br/><b>Campaign Setting: </b>General<br/><b>Prerequisite: </b>Elan Heritage feat<br/></p>Madness grows in the shadows, spawning new horrors to assail the world and corrupt it, twist it, and remake it into unspeakable forms. You are wholly consumed with destroying the menace of the Far Realm, though only you know what path brought you to the Awakening. Did you lose your people or loved ones to the aberrant menace? Or is your obsession merely intellectual, built on the knowledge that you must sacrifice yourself to stop this growing doom?<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<i>Associated Skills: </i>Dungeoneering, Perception<br/><p class=\"publishedIn\">Published in <a href=\"http://anonym.to/?http://www.wizards.com/dnd/Product.php?x=dnd/products/dndacc/210940000\" target=\"_new\">Psionic Power</a>, page(s) 125.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </form>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\n    if (document.all) {\r\n        if (document.documentMode != 9) {\r\n            var ar = document.getElementsByTagName(\'span\');\r\n            for (var i = 0; i < ar.length; i++ ) {\r\n                var c = ar[i].attrib