INSERT INTO `Background` VALUES ('782','Scion of Shadow','Campaign','Neverwinter','Arcana, Bluff, Stealth','Neverwinter Campaign Setting','0','\r\n\r\n<!DOCTYPE HTML>\r\n<html>\r\n<head id=\"Head1\"><title>\r\nScion of Shadow\r\n</title><meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=EmulateIE7\" /><link href=\"styles/detail.css\" media=\"screen\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" /><link href=\"styles/print.css\" media=\"print\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" /><link href=\"styles/mobile.css\" media=\"handheld\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n    <form name=\"form1\" method=\"post\" action=\"display.php?page=background&amp;id=782\" id=\"form1\">\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n    <div id=\"detail\">\r\n\r\n<h1   class=\"player\">Scion of Shadow</h1><p class=\"flavortext\"><b>Type: </b>Campaign<br/><b>Campaign Setting: </b>Neverwinter<br/><b>Prerequisite: </b>Human, shadar-kai, or shade<br/></p>As one of the Shadovar, you are most at home in the darkness, and you might know more of its ways—in either a mundane or a magical sense—than most. Or perhaps living among those who might consider you an enemy has given you a talent for hiding the truth.<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<i>Associated Skills: </i>Arcana, Bluff, Stealth<br/><p class=\"publishedIn\">Published in <a href=\"http://anonym.to/?http://www.wizards.com/dnd/Product.php?x=dnd/products/dndacc/317290000\" target=\"_new\">Neverwinter Campaign Setting</a>, page(s) 38.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </form>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\n    if (document.all) {\r\n        if (document.documentMode != 9) {\r\n            var ar = document.getElementsByTagName(\'span\');\r\n            for (var i = 0; i < ar.length; i++ ) {\r\n                var c = ar[i].attributes[\'class\'].value;\r\n                if (c == \'milevel\')\r\n                    ar[i].style.top = \"-24px\";\r\n                else if (c == \'miright\')\r\n                    ar[i].style.top = \"-18px\";\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n</script>\r\n');
INSERT INTO `Background` VALUES ('783','Devil\'s Pawn','Campaign','Neverwinter','Bluff, Religion','Neverwinter Campaign Setting','0','\r\n\r\n<!DOCTYPE HTML>\r\n<html>\r\n<head id=\"Head1\"><title>\r\nDevil\'s Pawn\r\n</title><meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=EmulateIE7\" /><link href=\"styles/detail.css\" media=\"screen\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" /><link href=\"styles/print.css\" media=\"print\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" /><link href=\"styles/mobile.css\" media=\"handheld\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n    <form name=\"form1\" method=\"post\" action=\"display.php?page=background&amp;id=783\" id=\"form1\">\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n    <div id=\"detail\">\r\n\r\n<h1   class=\"player\">Devil\'s Pawn</h1><p class=\"flavortext\"><b>Type: </b>Campaign<br/><b>Campaign Setting: </b>Neverwinter<br/></p>Many of your ilk have a silver tongue when it comes to deception, and you might be one of them. It’s also possible that during your admittedly short time in the cult, you picked up quite a bit of knowledge about faith in devil gods—even if at the time you thought it was all nonsense.<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<i>Associated Skills: </i>Bluff, Religion<br/><p class=\"publishedIn\">Published in <a href=\"http://anonym.to/?http://www.wizards.com/dnd/Product.php?x=dnd/products/dndacc/317290000\" target=\"_new\">Neverwinter Campaign Setting</a>, page(s) 41.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </form>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\n    if (document.all) {\r\n        if (document.documentMode != 9) {\r\n            var ar = document.getElementsByTagName(\'span\');\r\n            for (var i = 0; i < ar.length; i++ ) {\r\n                var c = ar[i].attributes[\'class\'].value;\r\n                if (c == \'milevel\')\r\n                    ar[i].style.top = \"-24px\";\r\n                else if (c == \'miright\')\r\n                    ar[i].style.